9:\"moderated_registration_denied_user_email__subject\";s:48:\"Your registration on {site_name} has been denied\";s:49:\"moderated_registration_denied_user_email__content\";s:243:\"Hello {first_name}: <br /><br />We just wanted to let you know that your registration request has not been approved. If you have questions about this decision please use our contact form to follow up.<br /><br /> - Your friends at {site_name} \";}\";','auto');
